    Scope and Contents
Papers of the Agenda for Action Committee (9174) including reports, proposals, working papers, drafts, and final reports of the committee, concerning administrative reorganization and implementation of the recommendations of the NCA Self-Study Committee.
The "Agenda for Action" Committee was charged with suggesting ways to implement recommendations "University in Process," the report of the North Central Association accredietation study.  This series includes memos, correspondence and working papers as well as te final report.  
  
